Title: fileinfo.groups: removed "Additional rules for files" functionality
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1606301740
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b1

The recently added "Additional rules for files" functionality has been removed
from the fileinfo.groups check. This functionality is not required as users are
encouraged to use mk_filestats to monitor files.
